text: The 2003 Sultan of Selangor Cup was played on 29 March 2003, at Shah Alam Stadium in Shah Alam, Selangor. == Match == Source: == Veterans == A match between veterans of two teams are also held in the same day before the real match starts as a curtain raiser. == References == Category:2003 in Malaysian football Category:Selangor FA Category:Sultan of Selangor Cup
